{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01RLmMvFKEf1besKEEHLRhw9","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Implementation History — 205-real-wallet\n     2→\n     3→Iteration log for the autonomous spec loop. Each entry records what was\n     4→attempted and whether it succeeded. The agent reads this file at the start\n     5→of every iteration to understand prior context.\n     6→\n     7→---\n     8→\n     9→## Iteration 1 — Build validation in real wallet mode\n    10→\n    11→**Item**: Set `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false`, run `pnpm build`, `pnpm lint`, and `pnpm typecheck`.\n    12→\n    13→**Result**: All three checks passed with zero errors. The pre-existing scaffold code (`RealWalletProvider.tsx`, `TestWalletProvider.tsx`, `WalletProvider.tsx`) compiles cleanly in real wallet mode. No fixes needed.\n    14→\n    15→- `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false pnpm build`: 423 modules transformed, build successful\n    16→- `pnpm lint`: 0 errors (10 pre-existing warnings in unrelated files)\n    17→- `pnpm typecheck`: 0 errors\n    18→\n    19→**Status**: Complete\n    20→## Iteration 1 — 2026-02-19T11:38:50Z — OK\n    21→- **Log**: iteration-001.log\n    22→\n    23→---\n    24→\n    25→## Iteration 2 — Shared ConnectionProvider across all wallet modes\n    26→\n    27→**Item**: Move `ConnectionProvider` from `RealWalletProvider.tsx` to `WalletProvider.tsx` level.\n    28→\n    29→**Changes**:\n    30→- `packages/wallet/src/WalletProvider.tsx` — Added `ConnectionProvider` import from `@solana/wallet-adapter-react`, added `getRpcUrl()` helper (reads `VITE_RPC_URL`, defaults to `https://api.devnet.solana.com`), wrapped both Mock and Real provider branches with `<ConnectionProvider endpoint={endpoint}>`.\n    31→- `packages/wallet/src/real/RealWalletProvider.tsx` — Removed `ConnectionProvider` import and wrapper, removed `getRpcUrl()` and `DEFAULT_RPC_URL` (now handled at `WalletProvider` level). `WalletBridge` still uses `useConnection()` from the shared pro